OL,3,CMayfair restaurateur found guilty of
OL,4,Cspiking woman's drink
OL,6,FA restauranteur has been found guilty
OL,7,Fof spiking a woman's drink with a date-
OL,8,Frape drug at a Mayfair private members
OL,9,Fclub.
OL,11,FVikas Nath put 'gamma-butyrolactone'
OL,12,F(GBL) into the woman's spicy margarita
OL,13,Fin a bid to overpower her for sex.
OL,15,FThis took place in a rooftop garden at
OL,16,FAnnabel's, a private members club, in
OL,17,FJanuary 2024.
