OL,3,CMayfair restaurateur found guilty of
OL,4,Cspiking woman's drink
OL,6,FAfter staff noticed Nath drug the
OL,7,Fdrink, they managed to switch it for a
OL,8,Ffresh one, before the woman drank from
OL,9,Fit.
OL,11,FSouthwark Crown Court heard Nath had
OL,12,Fgrown frustrated with the woman's
OL,13,Fapparent reluctance to have sex with
OL,14,Fhim prior to the spiking incident, and
OL,15,Ftook GBL in a vanilla extract bottle
OL,16,Fwith him to the club.
OL,18,FProsecutors said his plan was to drug
OL,19,Fthe woman and take her back to his
OL,20,Fhome for sex when she had been
OL,21,F"overpowered or stupefied".
