OL,3,CMayfair restaurateur found guilty of
OL,4,Cspiking woman's drink
OL,6,FToday, the jury found Nath guilty of
OL,7,Fattempting to administer a substance
OL,8,Fwith intent and possession of a Class
OL,9,FB drug.
OL,11,FThe businessman, who owns Michelin-
OL,12,Fstarred Benares in Mayfair as part of
OL,13,Fa collection of top restaurants in the
OL,14,FUK and Spain, could be seen shaking
OL,15,Fhis head in the dock.
OL,17,FHe wiped away tears as the judge
OL,18,Fremanded him in custody until
OL,19,Fsentencing at a later date, and could
OL,20,Fbe heard saying "That's bulls***".
