OL,3,CMayfair restaurateur found guilty of
OL,4,Cspiking woman's drink
OL,6,FNath admitted to spiking the woman's
OL,7,Fdrink after he was caught by Annabel's
OL,8,Fstaff and recorded on CCTV.
OL,10,FThe court heard that after Nath
OL,11,Frealised this, he threw the bottle of
OL,12,FMadagascar vanilla extract into a
OL,13,Ftoilet cistern. This was later
OL,14,Frecovered by the police.
OL,16,FProsecutor, Tim Clark KC praised the
OL,17,Fswift response of Annabel's staff
OL,18,Fafter they noticed "rather strange
OL,19,Factions" by Nath on January 15 2024.
