OL,6,F"(They) watched Mr Nath put a straw
OL,7,Finto (her) drink, sticking his finger
OL,8,Fover the top", he said.
OL,10,F"Nath had a small bottle in his hand,
OL,11,Fand used the straw to "suck up liquid"
