OL,6,FThe court heard they had been in
OL,7,Fcontact prior to the Annabel's
OL,8,Fincident, including for lunch meetings
OL,9,Fat Benares and the Beaverbrook Town
OL,10,FHouse five-star hotel.
OL,12,FShe also recalled Nath taking her to a
OL,13,Fburlesque show at Cirque Le Soir, and
OL,14,Fthe court was shown messages in which
OL,15,FNath had actually warned the woman
OL,16,Fabout drinks being spiked.
OL,18,F"I don't think I will be drinking
OL,19,Ftoday," she had messaged Nath, after
OL,20,Fan evening out.
