OL,6,FHe replied: "I think you should drink,
OL,7,Fbut be aware of people around you. My
OL,8,Fbiggest concern last night was someone
OL,9,Fspiking your drink."
OL,11,FAfter he was arrested at the club,
OL,12,FNath admitted spiking the woman's
OL,13,Fdrink without her consent, but
OL,14,Finsisted he had been trying to "relax"
OL,15,Fher rather than overpower her for sex
OL,17,FHe claimed to have obtained GBL to
OL,18,Fclean the wheel rims of a high-powered
OL,19,Fcar, on the advice of a friend, and
OL,20,Fsuggested he himself had drunk some of
OL,21,Fthe liquid in the past to relax.
