OL,7,Fkissed" the woman, but she denied this
OL,8,Fand told the court their relationship
OL,9,Fhad not been sexual.
OL,11,FIn texts shown to the jury, Nath had
OL,12,Fspoken to his friend about the woman
OL,13,Fand suggested that he would need to
OL,14,F"play the long game."
OL,16,FOn the day of the spiking incident, he
OL,17,Fwrote: "I'm at Annabel's. This is
OL,18,Fprobably the last evening with (her).
OL,19,FShe ain't biting."
