OL,6,F"Thankfully, alert bar staff witnessed
OL,7,Fwhat he was doing and were able to
OL,8,Fwarn the victim that her drink had
OL,9,Fbeen tampered with before calling the
OL,10,Fpolice.
OL,12,F"Despite his attempts to hide evidence
OL,13,Fand deny his intentions, we worked
OL,14,Fclosely with the Metropolitan Police
OL,15,Fto build a strong case to present at
OL,16,Ftrial, resulting in the jury finding
OL,17,Fhim guilty.
OL,19,F"Spiking is an incredibly serious
OL,20,Foffence that leaves victims
OL,21,Ftraumatised and fearful.
